@startuml
title UC10 - Backend Classes
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
class ProfileController { +getMe(req): ProfileDto +getHistory(req): HistoryPageDto }
class ProfileService { +getMyProfile(userId): ProfileDto +getMyHistory(userId, query): HistoryPageDto }
class ProfileRepository { +findUser(userId): User +getStats(userId): Stats +listHistory(userId, skip, take): {items,total} }
class LeaderboardRepository { +findUserRank(userId, month, year): RankRow }
class UsersController { +getProfile(req): ProfileDto +getHistory(req): HistoryPageDto }
note right of UsersController
  Admin support view, mounted under
  /admin/users/:id/profile|history
  (requireRole('ADMIN')). Delegates to
  the same ProfileService — no separate
  data shape for Admin vs self-service.
end note
ProfileController --> ProfileService
ProfileService --> ProfileRepository
ProfileService --> LeaderboardRepository : current-month rank
UsersController --> ProfileService
@enduml
